 genius coach\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"wife\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started running when I was 11, so it's not like I am couch-to-5k and then Olympic medalist,\\\" she pointed out, so it's probably right that we do here, too.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"couch\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"-to-5k\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"then Olympic medalist\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell left athletics in 2017, but not running entirely, taking up duathlon and winning a world age-group title as recently as April last year.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"duathlon\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"a world age-group title\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even now, her training is split, around 30 miles per-week on her feet and 100 on two wheels.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her training\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"week\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"her feet\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"two wheels\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, it is some leap from there (Ibiza, since you ask) to here, and a medal in one of the hottest 1,500m races ever run.\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2605, \"end\": 2610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibiza\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2169186274893761e-20, \"text\": \"Ibiza\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibiza\"