 2907, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was almost right, charging from last-but-one past tired women and to within sight of a medal rounding the home turn.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tired women\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"sight\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"the home turn\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crucially, though, she had expended energy bridging the gap to a leading pack that Bell had hung to from the start, tucked quietly on the inside, riding the danger line, saving every yard.\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"a leading pack\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3220}, {\"ngram\": \"the inside\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"the danger line\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"every yard\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell said afterwards that she began to realise a medal might be achievable as she cruised through the heats and semi-final with little fuss at her first global championships outdoors.\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"little fuss\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3435}, {\"ngram\": \"her first global championships\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The clues though, were there earlier in the season.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The clues\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3489}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the British Trials, she beat Muir, seven days before the Scot boosted the form by setting a new lifetime best.\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3539, \"end\": 3546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999966901640411, \"rank\": 2.5249085909267793e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Muir\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"the Scot\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"a new lifetime\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the London Diamond League, Bell ran 1:56.28 for 800m, faster than Hodgkinson needed here for gold.\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3653, \"end\": 3659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.5261944842124567e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 3660, \"end\": 3674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999712184480033, \"rank\": 2.878238027413459e-05, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 3715, \"end\": 3725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.7756721269923502, \"rank\": 0.28920450432744593, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://db