.\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chat\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Things have changed slightly.\\\"\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Things\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can say that again.\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 5198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4380, \"end\": 4389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999634826828016, \"rank\": 3.651722981606485e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 4480, \"end\": 4489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999634826828016, \"rank\": 3.651722981606485e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbped